@prefix foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> .

# Part 3: Reasoning over data using only FOAF ontology.
#
# Because exvoc:Photo rdfs:subClassOf foaf:Image and
# exvoc:depicts rdfs:subPropertyOf foaf:depicts, the EYE reasoner
# (with RDFS rules) infers that all exvoc:Photo instances are also
# foaf:Image instances and all exvoc:depicts triples are also
# foaf:depicts triples. This query therefore retrieves photos and
# depicted persons using FOAF terms only.

{
    ?photo a foaf:Image ;
           foaf:depicts ?person .
    ?person foaf:name ?name .
} => {
    ?photo foaf:depicts ?person .
    ?person foaf:name ?name .
} .
